node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Champagne Laurent-Perrier on September 17, 2021 tagging @coutellerie_ceccaldi. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
MATERIALS
Laurent-Perrier selects 11 of the 17 Grands Crus of the Champagne region from the existing 319 to create Grand Siècle iteration N°24.
@coutellerie_ceccaldi selects the steel, wood and horn used to assemble the knives.
#GrandSiecle #RecreatingThePerfectYear

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Champagne Laurent-Perrier on September 15, 2021 tagging @coutellerie_ceccaldi. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
MINERALITY
Grand Siècle iteration N°24 is an intensely fresh and complex mineral wine from the limestone soils of Champagne.
Stone is essential for sharpening the @coutellerie_ceccaldi knife, it alone gives it a perfect edge.
#GrandSiecle #RecreatingThePerfectYear

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Champagne Laurent-Perrier on September 13, 2021 tagging @coutellerie_ceccaldi. May be an image of knife.

node.text:
SHARP
The assemblage of Grand Siècle is supported by a majority of Chardonnay whose grape variety brings sharpness and complexity to this great Champagne wine.
Wet stones, oil stones, scythe stones, Japanese or even American made stones can be used to sharpen @coutellerie_ceccaldi knives to give them an exceptional edge.
#GrandSiecle #RecreatingThePerfectYear

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Champagne Laurent-Perrier on September 12, 2021 tagging @coutellerie_ceccaldi. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
ASSEMBLAGE
Beyond rare vintages, Grand Siècle, Laurent-Perrier Cuvée de Prestige, is a blend of three exceptional years with complementary oenological traits that recreate the perfect year.
The @coutellerie_ceccaldi knives are assembled from exceptional materials to create unique pieces and are true works of art.
#GrandSiecle #RecreatingThePerfectYear

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Champagne Laurent-Perrier on September 09, 2021 tagging @coutellerie_ceccaldi.

node.text:
KNOW-HOW
Grand Siècle was evolved in 1959 from the unique know-how of the House of Laurent-Perrier, with the philosophy of the art of assemblage: the assemblage of vintages, grape varieties and Crus.
The @coutellerie_ceccaldi know-how is manifold: the processing of steel, the carving of the finest woods, and the processing of horn. A craftsman's art, a unique know-how.
#GrandSiecle #RecreatingThePerfectYear

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Champagne Laurent-Perrier on September 07, 2021. May be an image of bottle.

node.text:
NEW LIMITED-EDITION: LAURENT-PERRIER CUVÉE ROSÉ BUTTERFLY
Bold creativity.
More than 50 years after its launching, Laurent-Perrier Cuvée Rosé still amazes us with its enchanting notes and intense red fruits aromas. Its unique and reusable champagne serving ritual has been reinvented for the 4th consecutive year.
#LaurentPerrier #ChosenByTheBest

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Champagne Laurent-Perrier on September 04, 2021.

node.text:
NEW LIMITED-EDITION: LAURENT-PERRIER CUVÉE ROSÉ BUTTERFLY
A poetically audacious breeze of freedom blows at Laurent-Perrier.
To take wing, to walk freely according to ones desires, without restrictions or barriers… To find the freedom that we have been denied for so long.
#LaurentPerrier #ChosenByTheBest

The ultimate symbol of our respect for nature and the environment.
Laurent-Perrier is preserving the biodiversity of the Champagne terroir, going beyond the environmental liability rules and complying with the Viticulture Durable in Champagne and Haute Valeur Environnementale specifications.
